The paper focuses on the field of text mining, which involves techniques for processing and analyzing large amounts of textual data. This falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses visualization techniques, which could be related to Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the use of machine learning and deep learning in text mining suggests a connection to Data Mining (cs.DB) and Deep Learning (cs.DL).
